\newcommand{\paru}[1]{\frac{\partial #1}{\partial u}}
\newcommand{\parv}[1]{\frac{\partial #1}{\partial v}}
</M>@}
<HEAD1>@{<E>1-form</E>@}</HEAD1>
dharA yAk ekTA @{<E>surface</E>@}  Achhe, tAr upar ekTA bindu nilAm, sekhAne @{<E>tangent plane</E>@}-r upare ekTA @{<E>tangent vector</E>@}  
nilAm. tAhale sei @{<E>tangent plane</E>@}-er @{<E>coordinate system</E>@}-er sApexe eTAke @{<M>(a,b)</M>@}  AkAre lekhA 
yAbe. ei jAygATAy mAthA guliye yAoyA swAbhAbik, tAi ekTA udAharaN niye egono yAk. 

<EXM>AmAder @{<E>surface</E>@}-er farmulA hala @{<M>(\cos u,\sin u, v)</M>@}  yekhAne
 @{<M>(u,v)\in[0,2\pi)\times[0,5].</M>@}  er upar @{<M>(u,v)=(0,2)</M>@}-r janya ye binduTA hay
 seTA nilAm, mAne @{<M>(1,0,2).</M>@}  ekhAne ekTA @{<E>tangent vector</E>@}  dichchhi
 @{<M>((1,0,2), (0,4,3)).</M>@}  ekhAne @{<M>(1,0,2)</M>@}  hala goRATA, Ar @{<M>(0,4,3)</M>@} 
 hala tIr~chihna-TA. mAne DagATA thAkbe @{<M>(1,0,2)+(0,4,3) = (1,4,5)</M>@}-e. tAhale er janya
 @{<M>(a,b)</M>@}  kI habe? absthATA nIcher chhabiTAr mata.
<CIMG web="cyl1.png"/>
<SOLN/>
prathame @{<E>axis</E>@}  duTo bAr kare nii. @{<M>(\paru x, \paru y, \paru z) = (-\sin u,\cos u, 0) = (0,1,0)</M>@}  eba.n 
@{<M>(\parv x, \parv y, \parv z) = (0,0, 1).</M>@}  tAr mAne kAjTA hala @{<M>(0,4,3)</M>@}-ke @{<M>a(0,1,0)+b(0,0,1)</M>@}  
AkAre lekhA. laxaNIya, ekhAne tIr~chihna a.nshaTA niye kAj karchhi. bojhAi yAchchhe ye, @{<M>(a,b)=(4,3)</M>@}  habe. 
</EXM>
AmrA ekhAne yA karlAm seTA @{<E>surface</E>@}-TAr yekono @{<E>tangent vector</E>@}  deoyA thAklei 
karA yeta. mAne yekono @{<E>tangent vector</E>@} deoyA thAklei AmrA @{<M>a</M>@}  Ar @{<M>b</M>@}  duTo @{<E>real number</E>@}  bAr karte pAri. 
ataeb AmrA likhte pAri @{<M>a = \phi(t),</M>@}  eba.n @{<M>b = \xi(t),</M>@}  yekhAne @{<M>t</M>@}  hala  @{<E>surface</E>@}-TAr kono @{<E>tangent vector.</E>@}  
ei @{<M>\phi(\cdot)</M>@}  Ar @{<M>\xi(\cdot)</M>@}-er ekTA b\oishiSTya hala ei ye, @{<E>surface</E>@}-TAr upar yekono bindutei
erA hala sekhAnkAr @{<E>tangent plane</E>@}-TA  theke @{<M>\rr</M>@}-e ekTA @{<E>linear transform.</E>@}  
 erakam @{<E>function</E>@}-der bale ei
 @{<E>surface</E>@}-TAr janya ekTA @{<E>1-form.</E>@}  
<P/>
ei dhAraNATA bAr bArai kAje lAgbe. tAi guchhiye sa.njnATA likhe rAkhi.
<P/>
dharA yAk kono ekTA @{<E>surface</E>@}  Achhe. tAr yAbatIya @{<M>p</M>@}  bindute @{<E>tangent
 plane</E>@}-TAr nAm dilAm @{<M>T_p,</M>@} (mAne sei bindute yAbtIya @{<E>tangent vector</E>@}-er @{<E>set</E>@}  
eTA). tAhale  ekTA @{<E>1-form</E>@}  mAne hala ekTA @{<E>function</E>@}  @{<M>\phi:\cup_pT_p\to\rr,</M>@}  
yeTA pratiTA @{<M>T_p</M>@}-r upare ekTA @{<E>linear transform</E>@}  hay. 

